---

<section id="about">
  <div class="section-wrap">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="section-num">01</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">About</h2>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-photo reveal">
        <div class="photo-frame">
          <img
            src="/images/sudhakar.jpeg"
            alt="Sudhakar Chaulagain"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="photo-label">Sudhakar Chaulagain</div>
        <div class="photo-sub">CS Junior · Security &amp; Software</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p>
          I'm a <strong>junior Computer Science student</strong> at Southeastern Louisiana
          University with dual concentrations in <strong>cybersecurity</strong> and
          <strong>software engineering</strong>. Originally from Nepal, I've
          been building things that sit at the intersection of security and
          software — from SAST tools that catch vulnerabilities at the code
          level to IoT health monitors that stream real sensor data to
          dashboards.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:1.25rem;">
          When I'm not writing detectors or competing in CTFs, I'm training the
          next generation — I taught Arduino and Raspberry Pi workshops through
          the <strong>Robotics Association of Nepal</strong>, reaching students
          who had never touched a microcontroller before.
        </p>
        <div class="about-detail">
          $ cat education.txt<br />
          Southeastern Louisiana University<br />
          B.S. Computer Science · GPA 3.86<br />
          Expected: December 2027<br />
          Focus: Cybersecurity + Software Engineering
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-right">
        <div class="info-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="info-card-label">Current Role</div>
          <div class="info-card-value">Lab Support Technician</div>
          <div class="info-card-sub">
            Dept. of Industrial &amp; Engineering Technology · SLU
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="info-card-label">Honors</div>
          <div class="info-card-value">UPE Honor Society</div>
          <div class="info-card-sub">President's List · 3.86 GPA</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="info-card-label">Location</div>
          <div class="info-card-value">Hammond, Louisiana</div>
          <div class="info-card-sub">Roots in Nepal · Open to relocation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card reveal">
          <div class="info-card-label">Focus Areas</div>
          <div class="info-card-value">Security Engineering</div>
          <div class="info-card-sub">
            SAST · Embedded Systems · Full-Stack Development
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* Profile photo */
  .about-photo {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .photo-frame {
    width: 220px;
    height: 280px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    position: relative;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .photo-frame::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(232, 160, 32, 0.15);
    border-radius: 3px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .photo-frame:hover {
    border-color: rgba(232, 160, 32, 0.4);
  }
  .photo-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .photo-label {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .photo-sub {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: 0.35rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .about-detail {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }
  .about-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }
  .info-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }
  .info-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(232, 160, 32, 0.3);
  }
  .info-card-label {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .info-card-value {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .info-card-sub {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .about-photo {
      align-items: center;
    }
    .photo-frame {
      width: 180px;
      height: 230px;
    }
  }
</style>
